Titolo: Immortal: Unchained

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Immortal: Unchained is a science fantasy action role-playing video game published by British studio Game Odyssey Ltd. and developed by Swedish studio Toadman Interactive for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One. The gameplay is inspired by the Dark Souls series, with a focus on futuristic firearms instead of melee combat, while the setting and plot are inspired by Norse mythology and the events of Ragnarok.